## Key Business Rules

1. Strike Escalation
- 1st strike: Warning
- 2nd strike: Temporary mute (1 hour)
- 3rd strike: Channel ban (24 hours)
- 4th strike: Server ban (7 days)
- 5th strike: Permanent ban

2. Permission Hierarchy
- Level 0: Helper (view only)
- Level 1: Moderator (temporary actions)
- Level 2: Admin (permanent actions)
- Level 3: Owner (full control)

3. Automated Actions
- Spam Detection: Auto-mute after 5 messages/5 seconds
- Link Filtering: Auto-delete blacklisted domains
- Mass Mention: Strike on >5 mentions
- Repeated Violations: Double punishment duration

